column2: SELECT m.objid, m.ra1 AS ra1, m.dec1 AS dec1, n.objid, s.specObjID, sn_median, e_bv_sfd, reliable, o.ra AS ra2, o.dec AS dec2 into mydb.spectrasn_final from MyDB.final_# AS m CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra1, m.dec1, #) AS n JOIN PhotoObjAll AS o ON n.objid = o.objid JOIN galSpecInfo AS s ON s.specObjID = o.specObjID
